commit 1167b1ff0671151fccec1ac0914bcc0b8bd436f4
Author: Marios Trivyzas <matriv@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Jun 24 17:03:45 2025 +0300

    Fix `c.r.allocation.awareness.*` settings to be visible in `sys.cluster`
    
    Mark the 2 settings were as exposed, and implement allow the implicit
    cast of `Settings` (because the `force` one is a group setting), to an
    Object, so that it can be transparently used in `SysClusterTableInfo`.
    
    Fixes: #18047
    (cherry picked from commit 3c5e054f07eb7f1a431a6c29766873a12aee5436)
    
    # Conflicts:
    #       server/src/test/java/io/crate/integrationtests/InformationSchemaTest.java

